window.docContents[210].resolve({"/______/____________/#pattern-fun":{"contents":"Pattern-Matching Functions可以通过模式匹配指定功能，方法是在 fun 之后编写一系列模式，每个模式前面都有一个竖线 (|)。这将脱糖为一个立即对其参数进行模式匹配的函数。\n\nPattern-Matching FunctionsisZero 使用模式匹配函数抽象定义，而 isZero' 使用模式匹配表达式定义：def isZero : Nat → Bool :=\n  fun\n    | 0 => true\n    | _ => false\n\ndef isZero' : Nat → Bool :=\n  fun n =>\n    match n with\n    | 0 => true\n    | _ => false\n因为前者是后者的语法糖，所以它们在定义上是相等的：example : isZero = isZero' := rfl\n脱糖在 #print 的输出中可见：#print isZero\n输出def isZero : Nat → Bool :=\nfun x =>\n  match x with\n  | 0 => true\n  | x => false\n尽管#print isZero'\n输出def isZero' : Nat → Bool :=\nfun n =>\n  match n with\n  | 0 => true\n  | x => false\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009条款\u0009模式匹配","header":"13.8.3. 模式匹配功能","id":"/______/____________/#pattern-fun"},"/____________/______--conv--___________________________/#conv-other":{"contents":"rfl closes one conv goal \"trivially\", by using reflexivity\n(that is, no rewriting).\n\nnorm_cast tactic in conv mode.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009策略样张\u0009使用  conv  进行有针对性的重写","header":"14.6.7. 其他","id":"/____________/______--conv--___________________________/#conv-other"},"/____________/______/#zh-basictypes-string-slice-h008":{"contents":"Obtains the smallest valid position that is greater than or equal to the given byte position.\n\nObtains the smallest valid position that is strictly greater than the given byte position.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009弦乐\u0009API 参考\u0009字符串切片\u0009API 参考","header":"20.8.4.11.1.6. 职位","id":"/____________/______/#zh-basictypes-string-slice-h008"},"/____________/______/#zh-basictypes-string-slice-h017":{"contents":"Returns the previous valid position before the given position, given a proof that the position\nis not the start position, which guarantees that such a position exists.\n\nReturns the previous valid position before the given position, or panics if the position is\nthe start position.\n\nReturns the previous valid position before the given position, or none if the position is\nthe start position.\n\nIterates p.prev n times.If this would move p past the start of s, the result is s.endPos.\n\nAdvances a valid position on a slice to the next valid position, given a proof that the\nposition is not the past-the-end position, which guarantees that such a position exists.\n\nAdvances a valid position on a slice to the next valid position, or panics if the given\nposition is the past-the-end position.\n\nAdvances a valid position on a slice to the next valid position, or returns none if the\ngiven position is the past-the-end position.\n\nAdvances the position p n times.If this would move p past the end of s, the result is s.endPos.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009弦乐\u0009API 参考\u0009字符串切片\u0009职位","header":"20.8.4.11.3.2. 递增和递减","id":"/____________/______/#zh-basictypes-string-slice-h017"},"/____________/_______________/#Fin":{"contents":"\n\n对于任何 自然数 n，Fin n 是包含严格小于 n 的所有自然数的类型。\n换句话说，Fin n 恰好具有 n 元素。\n它可用于表示列表或数组中的有效索引，也可用作规范的 n 元素类型。\n\nNatural numbers less than some upper bound.In particular, a Fin n is a natural number i with the constraint that i < n. It is the\ncanonical type with n elements.Creates a Fin n from i : Nat and a proof that i < n.The number that is strictly less than n.Fin.val is a coercion, so any Fin n can be used in a position where a Nat is expected.The number val is strictly less than the bound n.\n\nFin 与 UInt8、UInt16、UInt32、UInt64 和 USize 密切相关，它们也表示有限非负积分类型。\n但是，这些类型由位向量而不是自然数支持，并且它们具有固定的边界。\nFin 相对更灵活，但对于底层推理来说不太方便。\n特别是，使用位向量而不是证明数字小于 2 的某个幂可以避免需要注意避免评估具体界限。\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型","header":"20.3. 有限自然数","id":"/____________/_______________/#Fin"},"/_____________________/______Elan_______________/#elan-dir":{"contents":"默认情况下，Elan 将安装的工具链存储在用户主目录的 .elan/toolchains 中，其代理保存在 .elan/bin 中，该代理在安装 Elan 时添加到路径中。\n环境变量 ELAN_HOME 可用于更改此位置。\n应在安装 Elan 之前和使用 Lean 的所有会话中进行设置，以确保找到 Elan 的文件。\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009Build Tools\u0009Elan","header":"24.2.2. 工具链位置","id":"/_____________________/______Elan_______________/#elan-dir"}});